  "keyFeatures": [
    "Instant schema import via Smart Query (JSON metadata)",
    "Visual database diagram editor with drag-and-drop",
    "Support for 9 database types (PostgreSQL, MySQL, SQL Server, MariaDB, SQLite, ClickHouse, CockroachDB, Oracle)",
    "Multiple import methods: Smart Query, DDL scripts, DBML",
    "AI-powered DDL export for cross-database migration",
